description:
Online Q&A with an expert panel of Data Scientists to find out the latest in the world of Data Science and ask your questions.

Panelists

Terry McCann: https://www.linkedin.com/in/tpmccann/

Jan Teichmann: https://www.linkedin.com/in/janteichmann/

Gavita Regunath: https://www.linkedin.com/in/gavitaregunath/

Steph Locke: https://www.linkedin.com/in/stephanielocke/

Welcome back to Data Bristol! We are looking forward to in-person events, but until we can host them, we will do some online events to touch base with you all and catch up with some of our awesome speakers.

It would be great to hear some of your questions in advance so we can prepare some discussions with our panelists. Please send us a message with anything you'd like to ask.

Looking forward to seeing you there!

The zoom link will be made available when you RSVP. The passcode will be send out just before the event.

Thanks!
John, Anna and the team.
title: Microsoft Data Science - Panel Q&A
